summary: This document is a communication from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York transmitting a revised search warrant package to DNH. It indicates ongoing legal proceedings related to the Epstein case in July 2020.

events.title: Revised Search Warrant Package Submission

keyFacts: A revised search warrant package was prepared and sent by the SDNY on July 2, 2020.
The communication indicates ongoing investigative or legal activity related to the Epstein case in mid-2020.
The document is addressed to 'DNH', which is likely an individual or office involved in the case.
